Package: centraldog
Type: Package
Title: Replicate Central Dogma of Molecular Biology
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
  c(person(given = "Daniela Dana",
           family = "Danilova",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), # There must be a "cre", but there can only be one
           email = "s242794@dtu.dk"))
Description: Provides five functions to (1) create random DNA, (2) turn it to RNA, (3) find the codon, and (4) translate the codons. 
    The last function produces a plot that shows the distribution of the bases in a given sequence.
